abstract: >-
  A statistically rigorous benchmarking harness for LLM text inference on Apple
  Silicon (M5 Max), supporting comparison across backends (MTPLX, MLX,
  llama.cpp, BaseRT, custom Metal kernels) with reproducibility guarantees,
  thermal discipline, and custom compute kernel development.
